  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 167
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "As you exhaust all the questions you have for her, you thank her for
    taking the time out of her day to talk to you. She says it's no problem at all,
    and says that she had fun meeting and texting you!{wc}You say that you also had
    fun, before telling her that you have to go, and that you\u2019ll message her
    again later."
