  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "Ah, where do I even begin with this? I suppose my main hobby would
    be playing video games, as I have quite a big collection of them growing at home.{wc}Specifically,
    I like picking up life simulation games, but I also like the first-person shooter
    genre as well. I used to go to the gym too, but I haven\u2019t done that in years\u2026"
