  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 124
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "I don\u2019t, thankfully! I have a whole little apartment to myself
    thanks to my job, and it's right beside the university too, so I barely have
    to walk to get on campus!{wc}It truly is amazing what you can do when you don\u2019t
    have to worry about also taking care of other people!"
