  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 133
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: Ah, well I was originally from Canada! Was born and raised there in
    Wolfville, all the way in Nova Scotia.{wc}However, we moved to the USA when I
    was a lot younger, maybe 17 or 18 at the time? And we moved around the other
    states for a bit until we settled down here, finally.
