  itemId: 131
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "Why, of course I am! You can\u2019t just become a doctor through sheer
    will, now can you?{wc}Being in school is sort of what being a doctor is all about,
    and when you\u2019re not in school you\u2019re doing school work, or sitting
    in class for 4 hours for a horrible lecture, or turning in assignments\u2026
    I could go on."
