  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "Well, er, I might not have a job at this very moment, but it is for
    a good reason! I cannot dedicate myself to other {i}minimum wage{/i} jobs because
    I am pursuing my pre-medical bachelor\u2019s degree!{wc}And then I\u2019ll still
    have to go through more schooling\u2026 but, I\u2019ll be one step closer to
    being a doctor, at least!"
