  itemId: 135
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "Ah, my {i}parents{/i} asked me to babysit my younger siblings yesterday
    because they were having an emergency\u2026 or so they say.{wc}And since I was
    done with my classes and work shifts for the day, I really had no excuse to turn
    them down with\u2026{wc}I wish I did, honestly, but don\u2019t tell them that
    when you meet them!"
